        <section id="inspiration">
            <h2>Inspiration & Vision</h2>
            <div class="inspiration-section">
                <h3 style="color: var(--white); font-size: 1.8rem;">Role Model: Dr. Kevin Fu</h3>
                
                <p>Dr. Kevin Fu's pioneering work on medical device security has fundamentally shaped how we protect patient safety in connected healthcare systems. His research and advocacy have brought critical attention to the life-or-death implications of cybersecurity in healthcare.</p>

                <div class="quote-box">
                    <p class="quote-text">"Security in medical devices isn't just about protecting data‚Äîit's about protecting lives, because when healthcare technology fails, patients are directly at risk."</p>
                    <p class="quote-author">‚Äî Dr. Kevin Fu</p>
                </div>

                <h3 style="color: var(--accent-color); margin-top: 2rem;">Impact on My Career</h3>
                <p>Dr. Fu's research into vulnerabilities in implantable medical devices opened my eyes to the critical intersection of cybersecurity and patient safety. His work demonstrates that securing healthcare systems is not just a technical challenge‚Äîit's a moral imperative that directly affects human lives.</p>

                <p>What inspires me most is his collaborative approach: working with manufacturers, healthcare providers, and regulatory bodies to improve security without compromising the life-saving functionality of medical devices. He's shown that effective healthcare cybersecurity requires balancing security rigor with practical medical needs.</p>

                <p>His example motivates me to pursue a career where my technical skills can have a meaningful impact on patient safety and healthcare outcomes. I aspire to contribute to the field of healthcare cybersecurity with the same dedication to both technical excellence and real-world patient protection that Dr. Fu exemplifies.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

